reviewText:
California Dreams is DVD video of various girls posing and stripping. The video is very closely done in the style of Penthouse Magazine Video. The video has 10 different scenes covering just over an hour. (About 5-7 minutes per scene or girl) Some of the girls in this DVD are also famous models that have also appeared in either Penthouse Magazine, or from various adult sites. Such models include Angel Cassidy, Kayden Kross, Ginger Jolie, and Carli Banks, just to name some of the models in the video.

The DVD contains the movie, photo slideshow, and trailers for other "Peach Entertainment" or "Red Dragon Releasing" videos available wherever adult videos are sold.

Overall it's a nice DVD and good quality video. Personally I don't recommend paying more than $15 for this DVD as it's only just over 1 hour long. (1:05:26) FOR ADULTS ONLY!!!
I was expecting hard core porno. This is soft core or something akin to it. It is just naked girls posturing.
It's just a bunch of naked women squirming around. Which isn't all bad, but it's not for you if you don't care for strip teases.
